title: The Diligent Programmer
headline: Crook County High School Attendant | AP Student | Finished Code 201 | Growth Mindset Thinker
pitch: Hey! My name is Taytum and I've spent the last few years taking coding and app design classes. I'm interested in joining a team/job that practices diversity and is welcoming to everyone. My great teamworking and communication skills will be a great added asset to the team. Let's expand the world of technology together!
description: I'm excited to see what a diverse team can create with the available technology. Teamwork and communication are skills I've had to learn, practice and use throughout my entire life making me reliable in those topics.
